00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:20.200
healthcare domain and today I'm going to talk a little bit about how we made our healthcare

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:27.400
regulation a bit more shiny by making a dashboard which is modular and has layout-as-code so we can

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:35.160
accommodate different types of users and be compliant with privacy law and be developer

