friendly as well. Lots of promises. So first, if you think about healthcare regulation you

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:48.240
need to think a bit about healthcare systems and they have a tendency to be very differently for

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:55.560
different countries but we don't have the time to dive into that too deeply. So let's simplify

00:00:55.720 --> 00:01:03.279
