you're not allowed to see it. Also not very nice. So we had to kind of design layouts for the

00:08:22.239 --> 00:08:27.160
different user groups that we had. And you can hard code that, of course, in Shiny, but it's way

00:08:27.359 --> 00:08:35.080
nicer, I think, to define it in a separate way. So we went the JSON route and used a JSON file to

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:43.719
define the layouts of the various variants of the dashboard, let's say. So it would look a bit like

