00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:51.000
those chunks, a page module is instantiated, which has a modules field, which is an array of modules.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:56.520
And then from that, you can instantiate the tiles. And every tile, again, has a bit of the JSON,

