00:12:12.679 --> 00:12:19.239
module. So when graph module is running, it actually has sort of a pointer to the original

00:12:19.239 --> 00:12:24.840
selected ID variable inside the other module. So as soon as someone selects a different,

00:12:24.840 --> 00:12:31.320
let's say healthcare provider, then reactively things in the graph module will start recomputing

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:35.960
because they are reactively linked, like everything should be in a shiny app.

